block content
  .header
    h1 How to Play
  .content
  
    p.
      Kings, also known as Kings Cup or the Circle of Fire, is a popular drinking game played all over the world. 
      All you need is a deck of cards, a few buddies and some drinks to play.
  
    p.
      Please remember to <strong>drink responsibly</strong> and <strong>do not drive</strong> 
      after playing. Just stay where you are or call a buddy to come pick you up.
  
    ol
      li
        | Prepare beverages.
      li
        | Arrange the deck into a pile.
      li 
        | Draw a card.
      li
        | Read that card.
      li
        | Refer to the key below.
      li
        | Next person repeats step 3.
      li
        | Continue until no more cards are left.
    
