            h1.card-key-title Ten
            p.card-key-description
              strong Story time. 
              | Say a word. Next person says your word, plus another, while still forming a sentence. Next person says both words, plus another, while still forming a sentence. You get it. First person to mess up repeating the whole sentence or to blank out drinks. 
        .pure-u-1.pure-u-md-1-2
