            h1.card-key-title Nine
            p.card-key-description
              strong Rhyme time. 
              | Think of a word that's fairly simple to rhyme with. Go in a circle, each person naming a different word that rhymes with it. First person to blank out drinks.
        .pure-u-1.pure-u-md-1-2
